notes maturing on aug 15 and interest payments totaling about 21 
billion due that day 
also the united states most likely could not honor on aug 
3 3 billion of military retirement and salary payments or 
payments totaling over 11 billion to social security and 
supplemental security income recipients railroad retirees and 
veterans he added 
