wasnt being mentioned scougal said she was preparing what she 
would say to comfort her daughter words that never needed saying 
i was so amazed that i won because it was the first time 
said stevenson who clapped and looked around the stage for several 
seconds until she realized the master of ceremonies had announced 
her name as the winner 
