<TEXT>
only in poland did private farmers 
survive four decades of communist collectivization now they may be 
done in by the capitalisthe job mrs dole said at a news conference 
the rule will cover cars trucks and all other vehicles that are 
required by federal regulation to have seat belts 
automobile accidents are the single largest cause of 
occupational fatalities causing about 2100 jobrelated deaths a 
year she said 
